                        make them in black for slightly cheaper <a href="http://www.summitracing.com/parts/acc-4040k/overview/" target=_blank>HERE</a>.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        An HEI coil that has .6 or .7 Primary ohm value such as <a href="http://www.summitracing.com/parts/msd-8202" target=_blank>MSD No. 8202</a>. This is a 45,000 volt
